{"tid":1888362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"居家檢疫差一天解除　澳門學生出外買便當違規","createTime":"2020-02-20T06:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T03:52:31.000Z","uid":209657,"like":153,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b47968aa97a22120c7f99f6417b54fd3f96c7c","tid":1888362,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/19/3073582_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F19%2F3073582_1_1.jpg&h=13abcabf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屏東縣1名來自澳門的大學生6日入境後，被要求居家檢疫，原本今天就滿14天要解除管制，但昨天被防疫單位查到出外買便當，衛生局今天表示，將在調查事證後，依法裁處。<br />\n<br />\n衛生局副局長張秀君表示，衛生局今天已接到舉發單，指這名學生昨天違反傳染病防治法，在學生宿舍居家檢疫期間外出。張秀君說，這名學生因為沒有申請送餐，昨天自己出外買便當，被防疫單位透過手機定位追蹤發現可能離開宿舍，鄉長立刻帶隊前往宿舍同時舉發。<br />\n<br />\n張秀君表示，學生用餐問題，已由縣府民政處協助解決，後續會視情節告誡或開罰，依傳染病防治法第58條及60條規定，將可裁處新台幣1萬元以上、15萬元以下罰款。目前屏東縣居家檢疫者有448人，沒有確診個案，也沒有開罰個案。"},{"pid":"6ad3855e3e1e9cc7070874feaba1baa3401fee59","tid":1888362,"uid":209657,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/02/20/2416494-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F02%2F20%2F2416494-XXL.jpg&h=744c6a39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內埔鄉鄉長鍾慶鎮指出，防疫單位是透過智慧科技，對於居家檢疫者進行追蹤管理，村長也一再告誡檢疫對象，居家檢疫期間不得外出，尤其鄉內有兩所大學不能大意，尤其開學在即，防疫更不能馬虎，結果從手機定位中還是發現這位澳門學生擅離住所，所以才對他開單舉發。<br />\n<br />\n這名澳門學生很有可能成為屏東首位、違反居家檢疫而被裁罰的案例，屏東縣衛生局目前還沒接獲舉發，如有相關情事將依程序處置，會先要求該生陳述意見，並視違規案由情節輕重，依「傳染病防治法」第58條、69條規定，裁處1萬以上15萬元以下罰鍰。"},{"pid":"460722dc4dbeb6f0b42a1bef1d7d5e33cc8f32c1","tid":1888362,"uid":209657,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:02:27.000Z","msg":"便當1萬元以上"},{"pid":"652d4de2faa3392ca86e710ee631ee2180e6812d","tid":1888362,"uid":230416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"460722dc4dbeb6f0b42a1bef1d7d5e33cc8f32c1","tid":1888362,"uid":209657,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:02:27.000Z","msg":"便當1萬元以上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0403e0a9d40362c3b2d26af872fb45506a7daa0","tid":1888362,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"花開了，然後凋零。星星是璀璨的，可那光芒也會消失。<br />\n這個地球、太陽、銀河系甚至連這個宇宙也會有死亡的時候。<br />\n人的一生和這些東西相比，簡直就像剎那間的事情，<br />\n在這樣的一瞬間，人降生了，笑著、哭著、憎恨、喜悅、悲傷、愛，<br />\n一切只是剎那間的邂逅，而最後都要歸入死的永眠。"},{"pid":"d4b7aa19f3046874f149b2c913831422672c371f","tid":1888362,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:03:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=693194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D693194&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OffrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=77e0314e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D693194&h=bf1e7e57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=693194</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=692929&amp;utm_source=dable&amp;utm_medium=dable\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D692929%26utm_source%3Ddable%26utm_medium%3Ddable&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OffrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=1a5fe209\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D692929%26utm_source%3Ddable%26utm_medium%3Ddable&h=c2c42b1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=692929&amp;utm_source=dable&amp;utm_medium=dable</a>"},{"pid":"bebc94237dd97cb79286ef2b15f376170b07a351","tid":1888362,"uid":156511,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:06:45.000Z",